+		<title>
+		<function moreinfo="none">cfgt.list</function>
+		</title>
+		<para>
+		Lists reports info in memory.
+		</para>
+		<para>
+		Name: <emphasis>cfgt.list</emphasis>
+		</para>
+		<para>
+		Example:
+		</para>
